{
  "stem": "11589.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the reason is because they didn't have their freedom to write a book about the life in Russia, to paint a painting without a Kreml-- Kremlin, or to write music without, without Lenin and Stalin, you know, in the-- put it in the libretto, you know?",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's why, you know, they, they were not good for the Russians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's why they were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Where did--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I start writing to put together and all, writing a-- I say, if I, if I be alive and I come home, it's interesting to show my mom and dad, you know, and other people the life what was here.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still writing about these people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were nice people, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They knew about music, about literature, about everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I learned from them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I looked at them like gods, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not talking ?] the way they look.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally, they start writing a little thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this [? song ?] catches of them, of all these people-- names and all that stuff, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I liked it, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was a part of my life over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I walked out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had to do it, you know very discreetly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because Russians, you know, the guards, could see what I do, you know, and this and that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I did it, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Before we go too far, let me just ask you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "What were the living conditions like there every day that you were there?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Very bad.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What did you do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have enough, enough-- I mean, clothes to wear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, it's not comparing to a-- later when I heard about the, about the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's far away from that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't have nothing to wear.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
